msgctxt "6808"
msgid "Setsuko"
msgstr "Setsuko"

msgctxt "6812"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "6816"
msgid "Arima"
msgstr "Arima"

msgctxt "6820"
msgid "Shiobara"
msgstr "Shiobara"

msgctxt "6824"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "6828"
msgid "Talk_Ojigi"
msgstr "Talk_Ojigi"

msgctxt "6832"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "68_Setsuko"
msgid "Honey..."
msgstr "Cariño..."

msgctxt "80_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm sorry, Arima-san, but I took the liberty of looking into\\r\n"\n"your company's financial health."
msgstr "Disculpe, Arima-san, pero me tome la libertad de investigar\\r\n"\n"sobre el estado financiero de su compañía."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "The high interest rates you've charged are coming back to\\r\n"\n"haunt you. Refunds and defaulted loans have put your\\r\n"\n"business in a precarious position."
msgstr "Las altas tasas de interés que estuvieron cobrando ahora\\r\n"\n"les juega en contra. Los reembolsos y los préstamos incumplidos\\r\n"\n"pusieron tu negocio en una situación muy precaria."

msgctxt "104_Arima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "Even if you manage to get over the current hump by giving\\r\n"\n"your clients to Shiobara and putting his money into Tenjin's\\r\n"\n"pockets..."
msgstr "Incluso si lograras superar la crisis, dándoles tus\\r\n"\n"clientes a Shiobara y transfiriendo su dinero\\r\n"\n"a Préstamos Tenjin..."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "The demand for refunds won't stop, and you don't possess the\\r\n"\n"financial means to get new clients."
msgstr "Las reclamaciones por sobrepagos no se detendrán. Además,\\r\n"\n"ya no posees fondos para poder obtener clientes nuevos."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "Shiobara's funds will just barely solve the problem at hand,\\r\n"\n"and the only clients he'll inherit are the ones who can't\\r\n"\n"pay him back."
msgstr "Los fondos de Shiobara apenas podrán resolver el problema\\r\n"\n"y los únicos clientes que heredará son los que no podrán\\r\n"\n"devolverle el dinero."

msgctxt "152_Akiyama"
msgid "He'd be left with nothing but a bunch of deadbeats while\\r\n"\n"Tenjin Loans bleeds him dry. Your business is destined to\\r\n"\n"fail."
msgstr "Se quedaría solamente con una banda de deudores incobrables\\r\n"\n"que han utilizado todos los fondos de Préstamos Tenjin.\\r\n"\n"La quiebra de su negocio es inevitable."

msgctxt "164_Shiobara"
msgid "...!"
msgstr "¡...!"

msgctxt "176_Akiyama"
msgid "One bad streak is usually enough to keep the banks from\\r\n"\n"lending to you."
msgstr "Los bancos no suelen prestar dinero a una empresa\\r\n"\n"que ya tiene una mala reputación."

msgctxt "188_Akiyama"
msgid "Unless you reel in some new loans, Tenjin will go down in\\r\n"\n"flames and take Shiobara with it."
msgstr "A menos que puedas conseguir un nuevo préstamo,\\r\n"\n"tu empresa desaparecerá, y arrastrará a Shiobara con ella."

msgctxt "200_Arima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "212_Akiyama"
msgid "Setsuko-san knew all this."
msgstr "Setsuko-san lo sabía todo."

msgctxt "224_Akiyama"
msgid "She swallowed her pride and her honor, ready to scrub\\r\n"\n"toilets in a hostess club if that's what it took to pass my\\r\n"\n"test."
msgstr "Ella dejó de lado su vergüenza y orgullo, e incluso\\r\n"\n"se ofreció a limpiar los baños del club con tal\\r\n"\n"de poder pasar mi prueba."

msgctxt "236_Akiyama"
msgid "She was genuinely trying to make a new start with you."
msgstr "Ella realmente está intentando volver a empezar contigo."

msgctxt "248_Arima"
msgid "Setsuko..."
msgstr "Setsuko..."

msgctxt "260_Akiyama"
msgid "Setsuko-san, you've passed the test. I'll lend you fifty\\r\n"\n"million yen, like we agreed."
msgstr "Setsuko-san, has pasado la prueba. Como acordamos,\\r\n"\n"te haré el préstamo de cincuenta millones de yenes."

msgctxt "272_Setsuko"
msgid "...Thank you so very much."
msgstr "...Muchisimas gracias."

msgctxt "284_Arima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "344_Shiobara"
msgid "You really helped me out, Akiyama-san. I appreciate it."
msgstr "Akiyama-san, me ayudaste en esa situación. Te lo agradezco."

msgctxt "356_Akiyama"
msgid "I wasn't exactly trying to."
msgstr "No era mi intención hacerlo."

msgctxt "368_Shiobara"
msgid "It's just like you said."
msgstr "Como era de esperar, fue tal y como dijiste."

msgctxt "380_Akiyama"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "392_Shiobara"
msgid "Show people you're serious, and they'll be happy to work with you."
msgstr "Demuéstrales a las personas que vas en serio, y ellos estarán\n"\n"felices de trabajar contigo."

msgctxt "404_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "416_Shiobara"
msgid "Arima-san's wife was serious about passing your test, and\\r\n"\n"you responded to that."
msgstr "Setsuko-san lo dio todo con tal de poder cumplir tu prueba,\\r\n"\n"y tú respondiste a ello."

msgctxt "428_Shiobara"
msgid "I think Arima-san really understood his wife's\\r\n"\n"determination, as well."
msgstr "Además, estoy seguro que Arima-san pudo\\r\n"\n"apreciar la determinación de su esposa."

msgctxt "440_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "452_Shiobara"
msgid "My eyes have been opened."
msgstr "Abrí los ojos."

msgctxt "464_Shiobara"
msgid "I made a little bit of money and started acting like I had\\r\n"\n"it all figured out. I'll start over, and, this time, I know\\r\n"\n"my efforts will pay off!"
msgstr "Hice un poco de dinero y actué como si lo supiera todo.\\r\n"\n"¡Empezaré de nuevo y esta vez actuaré con seriedad,\\r\n"\n"dando todo de mí!"

